unavailable-subtitle: Tax rates are already too high.
choose-if: lower_tax_rates <= 5
on-arrival: budget += 2; workers_nlp -= 5; lower_tax_rates += 1; workers_nlp -= 5 if lower_tax_rates >= 2;

